Tuning:
Mem
Lock contention
IO 
CPU


Less Mem -> Less GC Pressure



Tuning vs Optimization:

C . T . R = a (constant)

C = compactness (how low is mem)
T = Throughput
R = Responsivness (Latency)


Tuning: 		vary C,T,R but fixed "a"
Optimization :  increse "a"



JVM: Young gen

eden -> survivor -> old

